- Tags administration (client)
- Settings (client)
- List tags and search on them with state (client)
- Fallback to OpenLibrary, Amazon API and throttle (server)
- Set a book as read/unread (client)
- Assign tags to books (client)
- Search on read state (client/server)
- Share book lists (client/server)
- No books placeholder (client)
- Infinite scrolling on books list (client)
- Loading spinner (client)
- Api key: POST /app to modify it, warning if no key at all (client)